{"type": "article", "id": 9982, "title": "呃，Google 给泰迪熊注册了专利", "description": "蠢萌，但半夜会动的泰迪熊机器人，你想来一只么？", "date": "2015-05-25T15:58:34Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 29, "name": "Top 15"}, {"id": 10607, "name": "智能泰迪熊"}, {"id": 199, "name": "Google"}], "category": 4, "author": 3630, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 19, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702103812yw62cVCxBZHJ0Wmt.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">Google 刚完成了公司历史<a href=\"http://pdfaiw.uspto.gov/.aiw?PageNum=0&amp;docid=20150138333&amp;IDKey=1EF5AB92E988&amp;HomeUrl=http%3A%2F%2Fappft.uspto.gov%2Fnetacgi%2Fnph-Parser%3FSect1%3DPTO2%2526Sect2%3DHITOFF%2526u%3D%25252Fnetahtml%25252FPTO%25252Fsearch-adv.html%2526r%3D20%2526p%3D1%2526f%3DG%2526l%3D50%2526d%3DPG01%2526S1%3D%28%28%252522Google%252522.AS.%29%252BAND%252B%252540PD%25253E%25253D20150521%25253C%25253D20151231%29%2526OS%3DAN%2F%252522Google%252522%252BAND%252BPD%2F5%2F21%2F2015-%3C12%2F31%2F2015%2526RS%3D%28AN%2F%252522Google%252522%252BAND%252BPD%2F20150521-%3C20151231%29\" target=\"_blank\">最酷的专利</a>：智能泰迪熊。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">这份专利是 2012 年 2 月申请的，今天公布出来。它是一个有着泰迪熊或兔子外形的机器人，配备有相机、麦克风、扬声器和马达，能实现有趣的交互。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n\t<li>\r\n\t\t兴趣：它可以张开眼睛、抬头、眼神聚焦在使用者或感兴趣的物体上。\r\n\t</li>\r\n\t<li>\r\n\t\t好奇：歪歪头、皱眉头或用手臂抓头。\r\n\t</li>\r\n\t<li>\r\n\t\t烦闷：眼神失焦向下看，拍自己的脚或闭上眼睛。\r\n\t</li>\r\n\t<li>\r\n\t\t吓一跳：突然坐下、站直或者瞳孔扩张。\r\n\t</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702103811VZ6QWzdokMR4lyCg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n<p>\r\n\t看起来很蠢萌吧。除了看得见的动作，它还能成为家庭设备的中枢控制器。通过 Wi-Fi，智能泰迪熊能够接收主人的指令，驱动其他设备做事情。例如电视、恒温器、天气预报、音乐播放器、窗帘、空调，都能够通过小熊来控制。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p4\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p5\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">这样一只蠢萌又有点小机智的熊仔，自然能得到小朋友的宠爱。不过对于成年人来说，不少人都说晚上看到它会感动害怕，尤其你还看过《咒怨》的话。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p4\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\">另外的担心来自隐私的泄露。智能泰迪熊能够记录小朋友的活动，但小朋友并没有保护隐私的意识。</span>而 Google 的人也说，很多专利是员工的奇思妙想，其实不一定会上市。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">\r\n\t题图来自：<a href=\"http://7-themes.com/6785338-cute-teddy-bear-wallpaper.html\" target=\"_blank\">7-Themes</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p6\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p4\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\">\r\n\t<span class=\"s1\"></span> \r\n</p>\n\n"}